#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:108
#: b95234c01f964ba084af99b44d7d47d9
msgid "The pipeline: from reference shape to physical integration"
msgstr "流程：从参考形状到物理积分"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:110
#: 9cd670ee631244589aca21362ca1de77
msgid ""
"Conceptually the element layer answers one question: *given a weak form to "
"integrate over a mesh, where are the quadrature points, what are the shape-"
"function values and gradients there, and what is the integration weight?* It"
" does this by composing seven static reference-element definitions with the "
"physical-space connectivity of your mesh. The overall flow is:"
msgstr ""
"从概念上讲，单元层回答的是一个问题：\\ *给定一个要在网格上积分的弱形式，求积点位于何处？那里的形函数值和梯度是多少？积分权重又是多少？* "
"它通过将七个静态参考单元定义与你网格的物理空间连接性组合起来实现这一点。总体流程如下："

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:150
#: 8d7ccd62749042b4b10b24494bca5f0a
msgid ""
"The rest of this section walks through every box and shows what the returned"
" tensors actually look like. All examples use :class:`~tensormesh.Triangle` "
"because it is the cheapest to print, but the structure is identical for the "
"other six shapes."
msgstr ""
"本节的其余部分将逐一讲解每个环节，并展示返回的张量实际是什么样子。所有示例都使用 :class:`~tensormesh.Triangle`\\ "
"，因为它打印起来开销最小，但对其余六种形状来说结构是完全相同的。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:157
#: 3064aabd9aa1477cb7b9a30ae4fd0ec5
msgid "Step 0 — Reference-element topology"
msgstr "步骤 0 —— 参考单元拓扑"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:159
#: f2198ac0d5934c1785ce7128c6724cf3
msgid ""
"Each subclass carries a handful of class-level ``torch.Tensor`` / ``tuple`` "
"attributes that pin down the reference geometry. Nothing here depends on "
"``order`` — these are just the corners of the reference shape and how they "
"connect:"
msgstr ""
"每个子类都带有少量类级别的 ``torch.Tensor`` / ``tuple`` 属性，用于确定参考几何。这里没有任何东西依赖 "
"``order``——它们只是参考形状的角点及其连接方式："

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:181
#: a426f513383440e78279721ccb78d6f5
msgid ""
"Two derived attributes worth knowing about: "
":attr:`~tensormesh.Element.is_mix_facet` is ``True`` for "
":class:`~tensormesh.Prism` and :class:`~tensormesh.Pyramid` (whose facets "
"come in two shapes), and otherwise ``False``; "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_facet_type` returns the facet element class "
"(``Line`` for a triangle, ``Triangle`` for a tetrahedron, the tuple "
"``(Triangle, Quadrilateral)`` for a prism)."
msgstr ""
"有两个派生属性值得了解：对于 :class:`~tensormesh.Prism` 和 :class:`~tensormesh.Pyramid`\\ "
"（它们的面有两种形状），\\ :attr:`~tensormesh.Element.is_mix_facet` 为 ``True``\\ ，其余情况为 "
"``False``\\ ；\\ :meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_facet_type` 返回面单元类（三角形为 "
"``Line``\\ ，四面体为 ``Triangle``\\ ，三棱柱为元组 ``(Triangle, Quadrilateral)``\\ ）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:191
#: 8060621359384c14bcf5060149b30333
msgid "Step 1 — Lagrange nodes (``get_basis``)"
msgstr "步骤 1 —— 拉格朗日节点（\\ ``get_basis``\\ ）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:193
#: 67b409ae5b034812a0ef003cf482b103
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_basis` picks where the interpolation nodes "
"sit on the reference element for a given polynomial order. The convention is"
" *vertex nodes first, then edge nodes, then face/interior nodes* — see "
":ref:`node-ordering-gallery` for the visual companion across all seven "
"shapes."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_basis` 为给定的多项式阶数确定插值节点在参考单元上的位置。约定是 "
"*先顶点节点，再边节点，然后是面/内部节点*——七种形状的可视化对照参见 :ref:`node-ordering-gallery`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:213
#: c9754c9c30334303a4cf8d8d623ccf66
msgid ""
"The output shape is ``[N_b, D]`` with :math:`N_b = (p+1)(p+2)/2` for simplex"
" shapes and :math:`(p+1)^d` for tensor-product shapes (quad / hex). Every "
"other step in the pipeline indexes into this layout, so it is the single "
"source of truth for \"what does *basis function b* mean?\""
msgstr ""
"输出形状为 ``[N_b, D]``\\ ，对于单纯形形状 :math:`N_b = (p+1)(p+2)/2`\\ "
"，对于张量积形状（四边形/六面体）则为 :math:`(p+1)^d`\\ 。流程中其余每一步都会按这一布局进行索引，因此它是回答“*基函数 b* "
"究竟意味着什么？”这一问题的唯一权威依据。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:220
#: aa9dcabcfd5b4a5190db534282d94476
msgid "Step 2 — Polynomial space (``get_polynomial``)"
msgstr "步骤 2 —— 多项式空间（\\ ``get_polynomial``\\ ）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:222
#: 52f407206d4d41f9a7891f7606f69831
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_polynomial` returns the polynomial space the "
"shape functions live in, as a :class:`~tensormesh.element.Polynomial`. The "
"space depends on the shape: simplex elements use the full :math:`P_k` (terms"
" with total degree :math:`\\le k`); tensor-product elements use :math:`Q_k` "
"(each coordinate exponent :math:`\\le k`); pyramid and prism use their own "
"ad-hoc spaces."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_polynomial` 以 "
":class:`~tensormesh.element.Polynomial` 的形式返回形函数所在的多项式空间。该空间取决于形状：单纯形单元使用完整的"
" :math:`P_k`\\ （总次数 :math:`\\le k` 的项）；张量积单元使用 :math:`Q_k`\\ （每个坐标的指数 "
":math:`\\le k`\\ ）；四棱锥和三棱柱则使用各自专用的空间。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:237
#: 209cc3a06e264b8c85047a86d91bd435
msgid ""
"You usually never call this directly — "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_basis_fns` invokes it for you. The hook is "
"meant to be overridden by people adding a new element type, so that the base"
" class can synthesise the Lagrange basis on top of a custom polynomial "
"space."
msgstr ""
"你通常不会直接调用它——:meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_basis_fns` "
"会替你调用。这个钩子是供添加新单元类型的人重写的，这样基类就能在自定义多项式空间之上合成拉格朗日基。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:244
#: f85bd901de5d497784890494aaa9c14e
msgid "Step 3 — Hat functions (``get_basis_fns``, ``get_basis_grad_fns``)"
msgstr "步骤 3 —— 帽函数（\\ ``get_basis_fns``\\ 、\\ ``get_basis_grad_fns``\\ ）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:246
#: c980fdc4c0464aad8cdb83623cc84b96
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_basis_fns` combines the previous two — "
"Lagrange nodes plus polynomial space — into the basis function set. "
"Internally TensorMesh evaluates the polynomial-space terms at the basis "
"nodes, inverts the resulting Vandermonde matrix, and pushes the coefficients"
" into a :class:`~tensormesh.element.Polynomials` (batched polynomial) "
"object. The output satisfies the Lagrange property "
":math:`\\phi_b(\\boldsymbol{\\xi}_{b'}) = \\delta_{bb'}`."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_basis_fns` "
"将前两者——拉格朗日节点与多项式空间——组合成基函数集合。在内部，TensorMesh 会在基节点处求值多项式空间的各项，对所得的 "
"Vandermonde 矩阵求逆，并将系数压入一个 :class:`~tensormesh.element.Polynomials`\\ "
"（批量多项式）对象。其输出满足拉格朗日性质 :math:`\\phi_b(\\boldsymbol{\\xi}_{b'}) = "
"\\delta_{bb'}`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:272
#: 25fb443faf0f4b468e23fb0670531b54
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The result of :meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_basis_fns` is **mesh-"
"independent** — every element in the mesh, regardless of physical shape, "
"uses the same :math:`\\phi_b(\\boldsymbol{\\xi})`. This is the entire point "
"of the reference-element trick."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_basis_fns` 的结果是 "
"**与网格无关的**——网格中的每个单元，无论其物理形状如何，都使用同一个 :math:`\\phi_b(\\boldsymbol{\\xi})`\\ "
"。这正是参考单元这一技巧的全部意义所在。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:277
#: 7a63e49e4a35434fb111f37126f2bc2f
msgid "P1 triangle shape functions"
msgstr "P1 三角形形函数"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:281
#: 5ae69abf048d4ff89410d958e5568b89
msgid ""
"The three P1 shape functions on the reference triangle. Each :math:`\\phi_b`"
" equals 1 at vertex *b* (red marker) and decays linearly to 0 at the other "
"two vertices."
msgstr ""
"参考三角形上的三个 P1 形函数。每个 :math:`\\phi_b` 在顶点 *b*\\ （红色标记）处等于 1，并线性衰减至另外两个顶点处的 0。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:285
#: e0b42113a4234b8fbb773e9a3d3e12b6
msgid ""
"For higher-order surface plots on every supported shape, see "
":doc:`/example_gallery/basics` (section \"Shape functions\"). Internally the"
" example_gallery scripts call exactly the "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_basis_fns` you just saw — there is no "
"separate plotting code path."
msgstr ""
"若需查看每种受支持形状上的高阶曲面图，参见 :doc:`/example_gallery/basics`\\ （“Shape "
"functions”一节）。在内部，example_gallery 脚本调用的正是你刚才看到的 "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_basis_fns`——并不存在单独的绘图代码路径。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:293
#: f65c08069aa14073a65d6c56544a9ba0
msgid "Step 4 — Reference quadrature (``get_quadrature``)"
msgstr "步骤 4 —— 参考求积（\\ ``get_quadrature``\\ ）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:295
#: c4c452e5f90249bfabf8d725fb7c9e83
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_quadrature` returns a Gauss-type rule on the "
"reference element — weights of shape ``[N_q]`` and points of shape ``[N_q, "
"D]``. The ``order`` argument is the *quadrature order*, not the basis order;"
" pick it large enough to integrate your weak form exactly. As a rule of "
"thumb, ``quadrature_order = 2 * basis_order`` is enough for most bilinear "
"forms on Laplace-type problems."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_quadrature` 返回参考单元上的高斯型规则——形状为 ``[N_q]`` "
"的权重和形状为 ``[N_q, D]`` 的求积点。\\ ``order`` 参数是 *求积阶数*\\ "
"，而非基函数阶数；要选得足够大，以便精确积分你的弱形式。作为经验法则，对于拉普拉斯型问题的大多数双线性形式，\\ ``quadrature_order "
"= 2 * basis_order`` 就足够了。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:310
#: 0fd980a7daab4b4db3c1e9b75df43c49
msgid ""
"Triangle, quad, hex, tet, pyramid, prism each pick a different rule family; "
"see ``tensormesh/element/quadrature.py`` for the tables."
msgstr ""
"三角形、四边形、六面体、四面体、四棱锥、三棱柱各自选用不同的规则族；具体表格参见 "
"``tensormesh/element/quadrature.py``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:315
#: 4d3ef1ec7ffe49a49a684f9a3bf741ac
msgid "Step 5 — Reference shape values (``eval_shape_val``)"
msgstr "步骤 5 —— 参考形函数值（\\ ``eval_shape_val``\\ ）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:317
#: 9f08de824d7d46b9bcdf1e6da6b5e205
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.eval_shape_val` composes Step 3 (basis functions)"
" with Step 4 (quadrature points): the resulting matrix has entry :math:`[q, "
"b] = \\phi_b(\\boldsymbol{\\xi}_q)`. This is still purely reference-element "
"data — no mesh has been touched."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.eval_shape_val` 将步骤 3（基函数）与步骤 4（求积点）组合起来：所得矩阵的元素为"
" :math:`[q, b] = \\phi_b(\\boldsymbol{\\xi}_q)`\\ 。这仍然纯粹是参考单元数据——还没有触及任何网格。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:332
#: 43eaac586d0147f0a19b7565d3266961
msgid ""
"Every element of every mesh, no matter its physical shape, reuses this "
"single :math:`[N_q, N_b]` matrix. This is the source of the FEM speed-up "
"over collocation methods — you build it once and broadcast it across all "
"elements during assembly."
msgstr ""
"无论物理形状如何，每个网格的每个单元都复用这同一个 :math:`[N_q, N_b]` "
"矩阵。这正是有限元方法相对于配点法提速的来源——你只需构建一次，并在装配过程中将其广播到所有单元上。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:339
#: 228a4acb439b4bc4a2b0b47d45a5a8cd
msgid "Step 6 — Cell Jacobian and physical gradients"
msgstr "步骤 6 —— 单元雅可比矩阵与物理梯度"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:341
#: 72a68b5a39624d7ebb6a45eb7bf6e345
msgid "Now the mesh enters. For each element :math:`e`, the isoparametric map"
msgstr "现在网格登场了。对于每个单元 :math:`e`\\ ，等参映射"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:343
#: 2cd26c955040411f99eaf2f26faa4aa9
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\mathbf{x}^e(\\boldsymbol{\\xi}) \\;=\\; \\sum_{b=1}^{N_b}\n"
"      \\phi_b(\\boldsymbol{\\xi})\\, \\mathbf{x}^e_b"
msgstr ""
"\\mathbf{x}^e(\\boldsymbol{\\xi}) \\;=\\; \\sum_{b=1}^{N_b}\n"
"      \\phi_b(\\boldsymbol{\\xi})\\, \\mathbf{x}^e_b"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:348
#: 94e38fe5368648f9bad74fa9d06f17aa
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"sends the reference element :math:`\\hat K` to the physical element "
":math:`K^e`, where :math:`\\mathbf{x}^e_b` are the physical coordinates of "
"element *e*'s basis nodes. Its Jacobian :math:`\\mathbf{J}^e_q = \\partial "
"\\mathbf{x}^e / \\partial \\boldsymbol{\\xi}`, evaluated at quadrature point"
" :math:`q`, is"
msgstr ""
"将参考单元 :math:`\\hat K` 映射到物理单元 :math:`K^e`\\ ，其中 :math:`\\mathbf{x}^e_b` 是单元 "
"*e* 的基节点的物理坐标。其雅可比矩阵 :math:`\\mathbf{J}^e_q = \\partial \\mathbf{x}^e / "
"\\partial \\boldsymbol{\\xi}` 在求积点 :math:`q` 处求值为"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:354
#: 99e0a2ad5f2a4632bb316068876e839c
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"J^e_{q,ij} \\;=\\; \\sum_{b=1}^{N_b}\n"
"      (\\mathbf{x}^e_b)_j \\, \\frac{\\partial \\phi_b}{\\partial \\xi_i}\n"
"      (\\boldsymbol{\\xi}_q)."
msgstr ""
"J^e_{q,ij} \\;=\\; \\sum_{b=1}^{N_b}\n"
"      (\\mathbf{x}^e_b)_j \\, \\frac{\\partial \\phi_b}{\\partial \\xi_i}\n"
"      (\\boldsymbol{\\xi}_q)."

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:360
#: ef8d4f4f16f349538cdef5205c38bcc3
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.eval_cell_jacobian` computes exactly this sum "
"across the whole mesh:"
msgstr ":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.eval_cell_jacobian` 会在整个网格上精确地计算这个求和："

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:381
#: b24554beb72b4b44ac79b237338c3680
msgid ""
"Physical-space gradients of the shape functions are then obtained by the "
"chain rule :math:`\\nabla_{\\!x}\\phi_b = "
"\\mathbf{J}^{-T}\\nabla_{\\!\\xi}\\phi_b`, which "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.eval_shape_grad` packages together with the "
"Jacobian it had to compute anyway:"
msgstr ""
"形函数的物理空间梯度随后通过链式法则 :math:`\\nabla_{\\!x}\\phi_b = "
"\\mathbf{J}^{-T}\\nabla_{\\!\\xi}\\phi_b` 得到，\\ "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.eval_shape_grad` 将其与本就需要计算的雅可比矩阵打包在一起："

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:401
#: 50dce603345944fa9da974763aeac9fe
msgid ""
"This is the first place in the pipeline where the **physical coordinates** "
"``element_coords`` enter. Everything before this point (``get_basis``, "
"``get_basis_fns``, ``eval_shape_val``) was pure reference-element data; "
"everything after it depends on the mesh geometry."
msgstr ""
"这是流程中 **物理坐标** ``element_coords`` 首次登场的地方。在此之前的一切（\\ ``get_basis``\\ 、\\ "
"``get_basis_fns``\\ 、\\ ``eval_shape_val``\\ ）都是纯粹的参考单元数据；在此之后的一切都依赖于网格几何。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:407
#: 46c0e314bc674a4590bc1e356f8a087b
msgid "Reference triangle vs physical triangle, with mapped quadrature points"
msgstr "参考三角形与物理三角形对比，附带映射后的求积点"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:411
#: 0f1f38a1956746019de736f4785d4d67
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Step 6 visualised on a single triangle. Left: reference element :math:`\\hat"
" K` with its three order-2 Gauss points. Right: a stretched, translated "
"physical triangle :math:`K`. The Gauss points are mapped through the "
"isoparametric map :math:`\\mathbf{F}_K`; values "
":math:`\\phi_b(\\boldsymbol{\\xi}_q)` reused unchanged from Step 5 are now "
"tied to the physical points :math:`\\mathbf{x}_q` for integration. The "
"Jacobian :math:`\\mathbf{J}` of this map drives both the gradient transform "
"and the :math:`\\lvert\\det\\mathbf{J}\\rvert` volume factor in the next "
"step."
msgstr ""
"在单个三角形上可视化的步骤 6。左：参考单元 :math:`\\hat K` 及其三个 2 阶高斯点。右：一个被拉伸、平移后的物理三角形 "
":math:`K`\\ 。高斯点通过等参映射 :math:`\\mathbf{F}_K` 进行映射；从步骤 5 原封不动复用的值 "
":math:`\\phi_b(\\boldsymbol{\\xi}_q)` 现在与物理点 :math:`\\mathbf{x}_q` "
"绑定以用于积分。该映射的雅可比矩阵 :math:`\\mathbf{J}` 同时驱动下一步中的梯度变换和体积因子 "
":math:`\\lvert\\det\\mathbf{J}\\rvert`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:423
#: 267144f5559a4d0b9ae929625531fa51
msgid "Step 7 — ``Transformation``: the cached package"
msgstr "步骤 7 —— ``Transformation``\\ ：缓存好的封装"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:425
#: 08b9c4c08ad841eead049308b9252d39
msgid ""
"In practice you never call ``eval_*`` directly. Instead you instantiate a "
":class:`~tensormesh.Transformation`, which lazily wires together every step "
"of the pipeline and caches the results as :class:`torch.nn.Module` buffers "
"(so ``.to(device)`` / ``.double()`` / ``.cuda()`` Just Work)."
msgstr ""
"实际中你绝不会直接调用 ``eval_*``\\ 。相反，你会实例化一个 :class:`~tensormesh.Transformation`\\ "
"，它会惰性地串联起流程的每一步，并将结果缓存为 :class:`torch.nn.Module` 缓冲区（这样 ``.to(device)`` / "
"``.double()`` / ``.cuda()`` 便能直接生效）。"

