#: 04dfb780153347d991ac354f558684ef
msgid ""
"For elements with mixed facet types (:class:`~tensormesh.Prism`, "
":class:`~tensormesh.Pyramid`) every one of these attributes returns a tuple "
"— triangular-facet quantities first, quadrilateral-facet quantities second. "
"The high-level ``FacetAssembler`` in :mod:`tensormesh.assemble` handles the "
"case-split for you."
msgstr ""
"对于具有混合面类型的单元（\\ :class:`~tensormesh.Prism`\\ 、\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.Pyramid`\\ ），上述每个属性都会返回一个元组——先是三角形面的量，其次是四边形面的量。\\ "
":mod:`tensormesh.assemble` 中的高层 ``FacetAssembler`` 会替你处理这种分情况讨论。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:533
#: be5d435cb8ee461b9506d61dac8c0449
msgid "The ordering convention"
msgstr "排序约定"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:535
#: 71038265376745ceb4ff500cc4410fc9
msgid ""
"TensorMesh stores connectivity for tensor-product shapes "
"(:class:`~tensormesh.Quadrilateral`, :class:`~tensormesh.Hexahedron`) in "
"**lexicographic** order — the order that matches the underlying tensor-"
"product polynomial layout. Gmsh and VTK use a different convention. The two "
"are not interchangeable for higher-order or tensor-product elements: feeding"
" Gmsh-ordered hex27 connectivity straight into the assembler produces "
"silently-broken basis evaluations."
msgstr ""
"对于张量积形状（\\ :class:`~tensormesh.Quadrilateral`\\ 、\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.Hexahedron`\\ ），TensorMesh 以 **字典序** "
"存储连接性——即与底层张量积多项式布局相匹配的顺序。Gmsh 和 VTK 使用的是另一套约定。对于高阶或张量积单元，这两套约定不可互换：将 Gmsh "
"排序的 hex27 连接性直接送入装配器，会在不报错的情况下产生错误的基函数求值结果。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:544
#: 96d1390574f04d1695c0171f00f48525
msgid "The single conversion point is :meth:`~tensormesh.Element.reorder`:"
msgstr "唯一的转换入口是 :meth:`~tensormesh.Element.reorder`\\ ："

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:546
#: 51a1c8d311f64f1e95bc14917b6da340
msgid ""
"``Element.reorder(elements, to_gmsh=False)`` — Gmsh/VTK → TensorMesh (used "
"when **reading** external meshes)."
msgstr ""
"``Element.reorder(elements, to_gmsh=False)`` —— Gmsh/VTK → TensorMesh（在 "
"**读取** 外部网格时使用）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:548
#: afe6cdcc4119466c806c51597e063930
msgid ""
"``Element.reorder(elements, to_gmsh=True)`` — TensorMesh → Gmsh/VTK (used "
"when **writing** ``.vtk`` / ``.vtu`` files)."
msgstr ""
"``Element.reorder(elements, to_gmsh=True)`` —— TensorMesh → Gmsh/VTK（在 "
"**写出** ``.vtk`` / ``.vtu`` 文件时使用）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:551
#: 426026a3b7314606b47f7f6687ed4c2b
msgid ""
"You almost never call :meth:`~tensormesh.Element.reorder` directly. The "
"high-level paths do it for you:"
msgstr "你几乎从不需要直接调用 :meth:`~tensormesh.Element.reorder`\\ 。高层路径会替你完成："

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:554
#: fbeab3f9b7714fa9b83cbe8c85baa951
msgid "The built-in mesh generators emit TensorMesh ordering already."
msgstr "内置网格生成器输出的本就是 TensorMesh 排序。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:555
#: f60703b75bb34791b5cf115e60adf6d6
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.read` and :meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.from_meshio` "
"accept ``reorder=True`` to convert on ingest."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.read` 和 :meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.from_meshio` 接受 "
"``reorder=True``\\ ，可在导入时进行转换。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:557
#: 46ec2ed43ed449068e26caaeb26c62ce
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.save` auto-detects ``.vtk``/``.vtu`` outputs and "
"reorders for you."
msgstr ":meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.save` 会自动检测 ``.vtk``/``.vtu`` 输出并替你重新排序。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:560
#: b9f19b95520f46b99debf03d36809537
msgid ""
"If you build a mesh from raw arrays (``Mesh(meshio_obj, reorder=True)``) the"
" same flag controls the behavior — pass ``reorder=True`` when the source "
"uses Gmsh/VTK convention. The example gallery has a side-by-side comparison "
"for every element type at orders 2–4: see :ref:`node-ordering-gallery`."
msgstr ""
"如果你从原始数组构建网格（\\ ``Mesh(meshio_obj, reorder=True)``\\ ），同一个标志控制其行为——当源数据采用 "
"Gmsh/VTK 约定时，请传入 ``reorder=True``\\ 。示例库为每种单元类型在 2–4 阶下提供了并排对比：参见 "
":ref:`node-ordering-gallery`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:568
#: ff1ee88cf5ab4ab3882207eeab640cde
msgid "Adding a new element type"
msgstr "添加新的单元类型"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:570
#: 58b4b0d345f6422bba05eafac2723d95
msgid ""
"Subclassing :class:`~tensormesh.Element` is the supported extension path, "
"and the pipeline above also tells you *which* hooks you need to override:"
msgstr ""
"对 :class:`~tensormesh.Element` 进行子类化是受支持的扩展方式，而上述流程也告诉了你 *需要* 重写 *哪些* 钩子："

