#: 322b210594074fe1bf9df0ede2c681eb
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_polynomial` — Step 2, the polynomial space "
"your new element lives in."
msgstr ":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_polynomial` —— 步骤 2，你的新单元所在的多项式空间。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:576
#: de027da8b844405c8df4132d30bd57a4
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_basis` — Step 1, the interpolation-node "
"coordinates."
msgstr ":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_basis` —— 步骤 1，插值节点的坐标。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:578
#: aa23885089854feb80fc171a6aaf7fac
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_quadrature` / "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_facet_quadrature` — Step 4 and its facet "
"variant."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_quadrature` / "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_facet_quadrature` —— 步骤 4 及其面变体。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:581
#: c910528e5b1e464cb1c21e5004fec274
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_facet_type`, "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_facet` — facet topology and basis-index "
"mapping."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_facet_type`\\ 、\\ "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_facet` —— 面拓扑与基函数索引映射。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:584
#: 60af5b565c874661b40c116ce382a419
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_gmsh_permutation` — only if you want the "
"element to round-trip through Gmsh / VTK files."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Element.get_gmsh_permutation` —— 仅当你希望该单元能与 Gmsh / VTK "
"文件往返互转时才需要。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/elements_and_quadrature.rst:587
#: 714ebb34235a44c481bf54b69ddc67dc
msgid ""
"The base class derives Steps 3, 5, 6, and 7 from those overrides "
"automatically. The existing seven shapes in "
"``tensormesh/element/element.py`` are short, self-contained templates; the "
"low-level helpers used inside those overrides "
"(:class:`~tensormesh.element.Polynomial`, basis-node generators, quadrature "
"factories) live under :ref:`api-element-internals`."
msgstr ""
"基类会根据这些重写自动推导出步骤 3、5、6 和 7。\\ ``tensormesh/element/element.py`` "
"中现有的七种形状都是简短、自包含的模板；这些重写内部所用的底层辅助工具（\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.element.Polynomial`\\ 、基节点生成器、求积工厂）位于 :ref:`api-element-"
"internals` 之下。"

